  "detailed_description": "\"Riddle Girl\" is a casual puzzle game in which all you have to do is replace parts of a picture, gradually building up a complete drawing. The game allows you to cheat, you can unlock any image after 25 seconds.<br>When you have completed the puzzle, you can view the finished images in the gallery at any time.<br>There is no time limit in the game for solving puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566910/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1635517513\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566910/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1635517513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1566910/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1635517513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2>▪  15 images<br>▪  Shuffle the fragments<br>▪  Cheat mode 25 seconds after starting the puzzle. <br>▪  Puzzles: 3х2, 3х3, 4х4 and 5x5.<br>▪  Your progress is saved in the gallery.<br>▪  Relaxing, enjoyable music<br>▪  Multiple soundtracks",
